Intsall urdf tutorial :

    sudo apt install ros-humble-urdf-tutorial

Do underlay workspace source

Go to /opt/ros/humble/share/urdf_tutorial/urdf

Do launching 

    ros2 launch urdf_tutorial displa.launch.py model:=/opt/ros/humble/share/urdf_tutorial/urdf/07-physics.urdf

Play around to see the features in rviz.

Use tf2 tools:
Install tf2 tools:

    sudo apt install ros-humble-tf2-tools
In a terminal run

    ros2 run tf2_tools view_frames

Check the location from where the above command was run. See the pdf showing relations.



